# Project Direction

Build one lean, premium, bilingual landing page for CEOs/COOs.

- Keep the page outcome-first: business clarity, decisions, risks, next actions.
- Do not turn it into a prompt-engineering course or a complex app.
- Preserve the static MVP: no backend, no AI API calls, no login, no stored user data.
- Treat `PromptAnatomy.app` as the mother platform and `ditreneris.github.io/lead/` as the sister proof platform.
- Primary conversion path: visitor gets an aha moment in the static clarity demo, then clicks to the full PromptAnatomy system.
- Prefer removing complexity over adding new features.
